    {
      "instruction": "<p>When the chips are almost done, drain the <strong>tofu</strong>, and cut the block<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> into three then each third in half again on a diagonal to create 6<span class=\"text-danger\"> [12]</span> pieces</p><p>Pat the <strong>tofu pieces </strong>dry with kitchen paper, sprinkle with <strong>flour</strong>, then tap off any excess</p><p>Dip the<strong> floured tofu</strong> into the <strong>batter</strong> and turn it several times until fully coated</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
